title: Wukong Bug fix (????)
body: So for ages now wukongs Q has been bugged where it won't even hit targets, which can be really frustrating as you need that q to land for maximum damage output, its been like this easily since 5.12 or so me and a couple of other players have noticed it i significantly noticed it with famous streamer "Nightblue3" when he played wukong{{champion:62}}

replies.body: BTW the title might be a little misleading for some basically i haven't seen anything in recent patch notes about this being fixed so i was wondering if recently you guys have come across the bug or if its been fixed hence the vote duhh :)
